### Step 3: Customize the statistics

By default, `gtsummary` reports median (IQR) for continuous variables. To switch to mean (SD), use the `statistic` argument:


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
diabetes |>
  select(diabetes_5y, age, bmi, glucose_mg_dl, bmi_class) |>
  tbl_summary(
    by = diabetes_5y,
